[[Image:Franz_Ludwig_Catel_-_Golf_von_Neapel_mit_Fischern_und_Muschelsammlern_(1850).jpg|thumb]]
两西西里王国是当时意大利半岛人口最多的国家，远多于其他邦国，其军队曾有10万人之多<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1dlob9r5TH0C&pg=PA77|title=Structuring the State: The Formation of Italy and Germany and the Puzzle of Federalism|last=Ziblatt|first=Daniel|date=2008-01-21|publisher=Princeton University Press|isbn=978-1-4008-2724-4|location=|pages=77|language=en|access-date=2020-03-25|archive-date=2021-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210705052607/https://books.google.com/books?id=1dlob9r5TH0C&pg=PA77}}</ref>。那不勒斯是两西西里王国的首都，也是人口最多的城市，同时是当时欧洲人口第三多的城市。国内的第二大城市是西西里岛的[[巴勒莫|巴勒莫]]，是意大利半岛人口第三多的城市<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RVoSBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA125|title=Italy in the Age of the Risorgimento 1790 - 1870|last=Hearder|first=Harry|date=2014-07-22|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-317-87206-1|location=|pages=125–6|language=en|access-date=2020-03-25|archive-date=2021-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210705055527/https://books.google.com/books?id=RVoSBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA125}}</ref>。自19世纪初起，两西西里地区的人口快速增长，自500万增长到700万<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/betweensaltwater00tomm|quote=kingdom of the two sicilies population.|title=Between Salt Water and Holy Water: A History of Southern Italy|last=Astarita|first=Tommaso|date=2006-07-17|publisher=W. W. Norton & Company|isbn=978-0-393-25432-7|language=en}}</ref>，到1850年占意大利半岛人口的36%<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=m_vOBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA18|title=An Economic History of Liberal Italy (Routledge Revivals): 1850-1918|last=Toniolo|first=Gianni|date=2014-10-14|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-317-56953-4|location=|pages=18|language=en|access-date=2020-03-25|archive-date=2021-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210705052657/https://books.google.com/books?id=m_vOBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA18}}</ref>。

